					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>The writing of this inscription seems to indicate the same period as the above. This records a similar gift of sheep for a lamp in the same temple by <hi rend="bold">Kūḷichchāni wife of Indamukki-Kōvaḍi-Kramavittar</hi> a member of the <hi rend="italic">āluṅgaṇam</hi> of the village. The <hi rend="italic">Peruṅguṟi-perumakkaḷ</hi> were to protect this gift. </p>						

						</summary>
